infographic sequence-steps-badge-card
data
  title ranctl lifecycle
  desc Every mutating action leaves evidence and keeps rollback explicit.
  sequences
    - label precheck
      desc config, host, policy
    - label plan
      desc render and rollback
    - label approval
      desc explicit operator gate
    - label apply
      desc mutate runtime
    - label verify
      desc steady state or fail
    - label rollback
      desc capture and restore
  order asc
theme
  palette #15803d #1d4ed8 #d97706 #ea580c #7c3aed #dc2626
  base
    text
      font-family Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui
